"AndroidAppDescription" = "QuickDrop is now also available as a separate app for your smartphone! Even though QuickDrop can also be used without a separate smartphone app, the app makes file transfer even easier and quicker. With it, you can even transfer files when you are not connected to your home's Wi-Fi network, by connecting the Mac to your smartphone's hotspot. The app still provides the same end-to-end encryption when transferring files.

